    "causal_summary": "Normalize every skill install-guide document filename to the single canonical form INSTALL-GUIDE.md (uppercase + hyphen), resolving three inconsistent casings (INSTALL_GUIDE, install-guide, install_guide). The doc-type identifier install_guide is a code contract and stays; the classifier gains additive hyphen-stem recognition so renamed files still type as install_guide rather than silently downgrading to readme.",
